---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "DeepSeek 使用技巧目录"
description: "DeepSeek 安装、提示词、接口接入、表格处理和代码阅读等实操文章目录。"
keywords: "DeepSeek使用技巧,DeepSeek安装教程,DeepSeek提示词,DeepSeek API"
permalink: /jiqiao/index.html
---
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">目录</p>
    <h1>DeepSeek 使用技巧目录</h1>
    <p class="tagline">从安装到日常任务，按真实问题整理，方便逐篇查阅。</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container toc-list">
    {% for post in collections.articles %}
    <article class="toc-card">
      <img src="{{ post.data.cover }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }} 配图" width="240" height="160" loading="lazy">
      <div>
        <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <p class="meta">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</p>
        <div class="tags">
          {% for tag in post.data.tags | readableTags %}
          <a class="tag-chip" href="/tags/{{ tag | tagSlug }}/">{{ tag }}</a>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
